PCA

Prep PCA

pca_rec <- recipe(~., data = penguins) %>%
  step_impute_mean(all_numeric_predictors()) %>%
  step_normalize(all_numeric()) %>%
  step_pca(all_numeric_predictors(), keep_original_cols = TRUE)
pca_prep <- pca_rec %>% 
  prep()

Inspect Results

pca_prep %>%
  tidy(3)
pca_prep %>%
  tidy(3) %>%
  visualize_pca_features(n_components = 2)

pca_prep %>%
  tidy(3) %>%
  visualize_pca_components()

pca_bake <- pca_prep %>% 
  bake(penguins)

pca_bake
pca_bake %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = PC1, y = PC2, color = species)) +
    geom_point()

UMAP

Prep UMAP

umap_rec <- recipe(~., data = penguins) %>%
  step_impute_mean(all_numeric_predictors()) %>%
  step_normalize(all_numeric()) %>%
  step_umap(all_numeric_predictors(), keep_original_cols = TRUE)
umap_prep <- umap_rec %>% 
  prep()
  
umap_prep
Recipe

Inputs:

Training data contained 344 data points and 11 incomplete rows. 

Operations:

Mean imputation for bill_length_mm, bill_depth_mm, flipper_length_mm, body_mass_g, year [trained]
Centering and scaling for bill_length_mm, bill_depth_mm, flipper_length_mm, body_mass_g, year [trained]
UMAP embedding for bill_length_mm, bill_depth_mm, flipper_length_mm, body_mass_g, year [trained]

Inspect Results

umap_bake <- umap_prep %>%
  bake(penguins)

umap_bake
umap_bake %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = UMAP1, y = UMAP2, color = species)) +
    geom_point(size = 0.1)
